high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink that's on your right so you are standing in front of it facing it.
Pick up the black plate that's in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge that's on your left and stand in front of it facing it.
Cool the plate in the fridge and then take it back out and close the door.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink that you see on the left.
Pick up the dark plate that is sitting in the sink.
Turn around completely and walk towards the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge, sit the plate on the bottom shelf, close the fridge door, and open it a few moments later to take the chilled plate back out.
Turn to your left and walk back over to the sink.
Place the plate back into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled plate back into the sink where it came from.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the sink.
Take the plate out of the sink.
Go to the right and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the plate on the bottom shelf of the fridge, close the door, open the door and take the plate out and shut the door.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed plate in the sink.
